{"tid":2265561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣200日本土零感染　9月餐飲營業歷年新高　第3季經濟成長3.33%","createTime":"2020-10-31T14:12:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T15:49:25.000Z","uid":261647,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbf87770bb480f456bb61b7640b84d83e8e5b03","tid":2265561,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/memepowertw/photos/a.111854536816745/359565788712284/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmemepowertw%2Fphotos%2Fa.111854536816745%2F359565788712284%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=0999b004\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/memepowertw/photos/a.111854536816745/359565788712284/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n經濟部前日開記者會公布數據<br />\n<br />\n１．2289萬人領取，領取率達96.1％。<br />\n<br />\n２．7月15號三倍券一發．零售業馬上在7月終止連續5個月負成長，8月9月創歷年新高<br />\n<br />\n３．餐飲業8月起營業額轉正，9月創下歷年新高<br />\n<br />\n４．三倍券原本粗估最低有700億商機，現在看來比預設目標1000億還要好。<br />\n<br />\n５．從數位綁定三倍券來看，民眾領3000，平均消費竟然高達6,000元<br />\n<br />\n６．三倍券預估拉高台灣2020經濟成長超過1.76%，台灣第3季經濟成長率竟高達3.33%"},{"pid":"0a17d5e5b006679f1b70587b526c462b5f98f1a8","tid":2265561,"uid":323740,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"好想去台灣瘋狂旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4902bf9b9de5b15e4976d5360cc510aac2fd11c","tid":2265561,"uid":274435,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"2020最強國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9cf06b73fcad5914a5b54cd0f52198d0ddd0c7","tid":2265561,"uid":12991,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"自己國家自己救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/